---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="czap showcase -- SSE streaming">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Streaming Adaptive UI</h1>
    <p>
      Server-Sent Events drive real-time morphing. The container below subscribes
      to <code>/api/feed</code> and adaptively renders incoming events as they arrive.
    </p>
  </header>

  <section class="stream-demo">
    <div
      class="stream-container"
      data-czap-stream-url="/api/feed"
      client:stream
    >
      <p class="stream-placeholder">Waiting for events from SSE feed...</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="explanation">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>The <code>data-czap-stream-url</code> attribute points to an SSE endpoint.</li>
      <li>The <code>client:stream</code> directive hydrates the container with the czap SSE client.</li>
      <li>Each event payload is morphed into the DOM using the czap morph algorithm -- minimal diffing, no full re-render.</li>
      <li>Boundary state changes (e.g. viewport resize) are applied to streamed content in real time.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--czap-primary, #4f46e5);
  }
  .page-header p {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--czap-muted, #64748b);
    max-width: 40rem;
  }
  .page-header code {
    background: var(--czap-border, #e2e8f0);
    padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.85em;
  }

  .stream-demo {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .stream-container {
    min-height: 12rem;
    border: 2px dashed var(--czap-border, #e2e8f0);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--czap-surface, #ffffff) 95%, var(--czap-primary, #4f46e5));
  }

  .stream-placeholder {
    color: var(--czap-muted, #64748b);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .explanation {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .explanation h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .explanation ol {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--czap-muted, #64748b);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }
  .explanation code {
    background: var(--czap-border, #e2e8f0);
    padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.85em;
  }
</style>
